block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #{title}
  form(action='/saveForm', method='post')
    
    label 
      | Name:
      input(name='name')
    
    label 
      | Date:
      input(name='signature_date', type='date')
      
    label 
      | Treating/Referring Physician Name:
      input(name='physician_name')
      
    label 
      | Street Address:
      input(name='address')
      
    label
      | City:
      input(name='city')
      
    label
      | State:
      input(name='state')
      
    label
      | Zip:
      input(name='zip')
      
    label
      | Phone Number:
      input(name='phone')
      
     p
     | BY ENGAGING OUR SERVICES, YOU ACKNOWLEDGE AND AGREE TO ASSUME THE RISK OF THESE LIMITATIONS. 
     | YOU FURTHER UNDERSTAND THAT NO WARRANTY OR GUARANTEE HAS BEEN MADE TO YOU CONCERNING ANY 
     | PARTICULAR RESULT OR CURE OF YOUR CONDITION.

    label
      | Signature:
      input(name='disclaimer_signature')
     
    label
      | Date:
      input(name='disclaimer_date', type='date')
      
    label
      | What is your diagnoses/disease/disorder in question:
      textarea(name='diagnoses')
      
    label
